{
  "schema": "exploration_corpora_v1",
  "forge_version": "1",
  "comment": [
    "Stage-1 exploration corpora. Each entry names a LOCAL source checkout and the",
    "commit it is pinned to; the forge exports that commit with `git archive` and",
    "never writes back into the source.",
    "",
    "Generated corpora land under benchmarks/repo-qa/.work/exploration/ which is",
    "gitignored: corpus contents are NEVER vendored into git, only regenerated from",
    "(source commit, forge version, seed).",
    "",
    "mutable_roots bound the blast radius. Directory renames only apply STRICTLY",
    "BELOW a root, so the root itself stays a stable anchor for the import rewriter.",
    "validation is the oracle: a corpus that fails it is never marked ready."
  ],
  "corpora": [
